  C:\Users\CH\AppData\Local\atom\bin;
  C:\Program Files\Microsoft VS Code\bin
// Register Anaconda as my default Python 3.6 *
(4) Install Microsoft VSCode

2. cmd终端窗口属性设置
(1) [字体] => [大小：10 x 20]
(2) [布局] => [屏幕缓冲区大小：100/100] => [窗口大小：100/30] => [窗口位置：100/30]
(3) [颜色] => [屏幕文字：第3绿色]

3. 更换国内源
